        "content": "<p>Out of curiosity, why is <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Finsupp.degree#doc\">docs#Finsupp.degree</a> called that? I would have expected that name to be used for <code>f.support.max</code> or something similar.</p>",
